<br>
This will be the most worthless long-term war.  Nothing will be solved except the killing of a leader and his regime.  And in the long term, that won't even change anything, because in the Middle East...Might makes right!  The person with the most military power will soon have complete power.  The next regime like Saddam's is right around the corner.  Iraq isn't going to fucking become Disneyland because Saddam is ousted.<br>
<br>
