<br>
You can't police the world in the 21st century.  Some things are beyond (and should be) our control.  We need to focus on getting OUR country through the hard times.  We need to focus on OUR children and how to help them become intelligent, compassionate, and thought driven adults that will help save America and the world in the future.<br>
<br>
In closing...If this was only about Saddam, he would already be dead.  Our intelligence community would have been able to take him out a long time ago.  One sniper shot through the frontal lobe and Saddam is no more.<br>
<br>
To be honest I don't know where I stand on this.  I don't really know if the US is abusing their military power over a weaker country, creating a &quot;Valid Reason&quot; to help out our nation by hurting another.  I would love to believe that the US is trying to help Iraq by geting hid of Saddam, but if that is the case, then why isn't he dead already?<br>
<br>
I do want to thank our soldiers in the military that VOLUNTEER to watch our borders and let the rest of us sleep safe at night knowing you are doing so.  I just hope you and your lives are not being wasted and abused for economic reasons.<br>
<br>
We will see...<br>
